data.description: Seller offering $9k on concession for your 3-2-1 interest rate buy down to help you save on your monthly payment. Washer, Dryer, and Fridge are included in the sale of this home. Well-kept, 2-year-old, Pulte home with an open concept, perfect for entertaining! As you walk in the house find 2 bedrooms with a full bath to your left. Take a few steps in the wide foyer into the flex space. Spacious laundry room tucked away near the garage. The primary bedroom is located on the opposite side of the additional bedrooms for privacy, with a big walk-in closet. Primary bathroom with standing shower and his and her sinks. The kitchen features durable granite countertops.  10-year foundation warranty. The features of the house are attached to the transaction desk. Contact me to connect you to a lender offering a 3-2-1 buy-down program.
